entries.femaleVariant: I did not get Nash, who was not in Rocky Ridge. The fucker didn't show.
Panam...
I know where their little hidey-hole is.
They will not be expecting us. I'm sure of it.
Listen, V. It's not over yet.
Fine. Where's this den?
No. Not what we agreed.
All right... So where's this hideout?
A hop and skip away.
No. Not what we agreed.
Are you joking? Tell me you are, please.
It's not? You got the cargo, you got your car…
Listen, I have a plan.
And I don't care. The car and the merch – that's what we were after. We got them. Sixth Street awaits word, and I…
Nash hunt wasn't part of the deal.
Let's do the 6th Street deal first.
OK. So where's this hideout?
A Nash hunt wasn't part of our deal.
Let's do the deal with Sixth Street first. We can talk about Nash later.
Only because I thought he would show up in Rocky Ridge!
Do you really not understand that?
You wanna raid the Raffen base? Are you outta your mind?
Wanna just show up at the Raffen hideout? Are you out of your mind?
I KNOW he's there. V! That fucking Raffen cheated me. I can't just let it go, I can't.
But he didn't. Might not even be in their hideout.
Later? When? After he hears all about the show at Rocky Ridge? If we go now, we can still take him by surprise!
You really wanna raid the Raffens' den NOW? Holdin' the merch you literally just got back?
The cargo will be fine.
V – I have to do this. Do you understand?!
Do you have a better idea? Let me hear it!
Matter of fact, I do. We take the stuff to Sixth Street, then go after Hellman like we planned!
I gave you my word, didn't I? Please stop riding my ass about Hellman!
And do not start acting high and mighty like you won't lift a finger if it's not in the contract. Just… just help me get Nash.
Thanks, V.
Not about to risk everything to settle a score that isn't even mine.
You don't get it. This is more than just...
No, Panam. Nash made a fool of you, I get it. But don't try an' make one out of me.
We hand the goods off to Sixth Street, then set up the Hellman grab. That was our deal.
That was our deal.
We'll take the old, unfinished freeway nearby.
See? Managed just fine without Mitch and Scorpion.
Think I see where this is going...
So it was about vengeance. The whole time.
Oh, you're on a vengeance kick.
Just listen to me, for fuck's sake!
The hell you know about me!
Either you're not bein' straight with me, or you don't know what you want. Hard to say which is worse.
